title: about

Football Ball kevin









I played football at Ball State University in Muncie, Indiana. I had a ton of fun. My seinor year, I was elected a captain by my teammates, which is an accomplishment I hold very dearly.

I loved living in Muncie. Most folks find this strange!

For a while, I was incredibly glad to be done playing. I’m now ~5 years out and am beginning to miss it.

..or maybe I am just forgetting the injuries…
